OL,5, The parents of a three-year-old boy who
OL,6, wandered home from school alone are    
OL,7, demanding answers from the authorities.
OL,9,FGeorgia Wilcox said her family were    
OL,10,Fshocked when Miles turned up at their  
OL,11,Fhome in Trealaw, near Tonypandy,       
OL,12,FRhondda Cynon Taf, during school time. 
OL,14,FA woman followed Miles, who is         
OL,15,Fnon-verbal, to make sure he got home   
OL,16,Fafter being spotted walking alone.     
OL,18,FRhondda Cynon Taf Council said a full  
OL,19,Finvestigation into the "serious        
OL,20,Fincident" was under way.               
